            <div class="grid-img__content">
                <p class="dropcap">The idea behind the Vacation Planner was to take our biggest destinations and create a travel package around it. You would go in, select dates and tickets for the main attraction, something like Disneyland for example, and then you would be presented with discounted offers to things like restaurants that you could add to your booking. At the end of the process you are emailed a PDF with information about the main attraction, all of your tickets, and accessories to customer support if you need it.</p>
