        </div>
        <div class="grid-main__content grid-main__content--narrow">
            <p>The three main components to build around this project were the marketing pages for the main attractions, the travel booking creation process, and the PDF and followup emails after someone has finished their purchase. For the marketing pages, we created a data set for each package centered around a main attraction that had a set of images,  graphics, and promotional materials such as videos and maps of the park. This data powered all of the marketing pages for each attraction we added.</p>
